title: McKenzie Made
overview: Award-winning director Red Ezra presents AVN's Best New Starlet McKenzie Lee in her first film as a Club Jenna contract girl and this British sensation is not to be taken lightly. Ride along with her as she seduces Reno in the back of a semi, then lures Nick Manning and Katie Morgan into the stickest threesome ever captured on film. Passions ignite in a garage full of sports cars as Barrett Blade teaches the alluring Kirsten Price to drive his stick. While naughty girl Jezebelle Bond breaks out her skates as Justin Syder gives her the rollerfucking of a lifetime. With sets and shots as beautiful as the girls themselves, this is one sexual journey you won't soon forget! Is your sex drive ready?
